source: TEXT_CTSMYCENTRANCENORMAL_00705_A3_000_001<tab>Ask about conditions on the Bozjan southern front.
TEXT_CTSMYCENTRANCENORMAL_00705_SERAOUSH_000_000<tab>I daresay there is not a soldier in all of the Resistance who has yet to hear of your exploits on the southern front.
TEXT_CTSMYCENTRANCENORMAL_00705_SYSTEM_000_001<tab>You are Resistance rank <var 20 E802 /var>, and have amassed <var 22 E803 ((,)) /var> mettle.
TEXT_CTSMYCENTRANCENORMAL_00705_SYSTEM_000_005<tab>Please note that you have reached the maximum Resistance rank.
TEXT_CTSMYCENTRANCENORMAL_00705_SYSTEM_000_010<tab><var 22 E802 ((,)) /var> mettle is required to reach the next Resistance rank.
TEXT_CTSMYCENTRANCENORMAL_00705_SYSTEM_000_015<tab>You have earned sufficient mettle to increase Resistance rank. Report to the Resistance commander on the Bozjan southern front.
TEXT_CTSMYCENTRANCENORMAL_00705_MIKOTO_000_100<tab>If only I had remembered what Misija did to me. I recall a strange device and being tied down, but sadly the rest is a haze...

TEXT_CTSMYCENTRANCENORMAL_00705_MIKOTO_000_101<tab>That she would go to such lengths to lay claim to those ruins can only mean one thing─a store of crystals with the capacity to power Save the Queen must lie within.
TEXT_CTSMYCENTRANCENORMAL_00705_MIKOTO_000_102<tab>Please, you must stop her! If she should bring the blade's full might to bear, all hope is lost!
